						| Oklahoma, but due to electrical issues with the building, the decision was made to relocate the shop to Tahlequah
						| Oklahoma. theBRATcrew LLC is a family owned and operated business, which will soon include not only BRAT Vapor
						| locations, but BRAT Vapor Wholesale warehouses as well.
