						br
						|                     BRAT Juice is a smooth 80/20 vg over pg mix with the maximum allowed flavor content. BRAT Vapor rents our ISO certified
						|                                   lab space to mix this unbelievably awesome juice. No food coloring or other additives are mixed into our juice. Our
						|                                   sweet flavors are sweet due to the flavor recipes we use.
						br
