						|                     This site was designed and integrated by Richard Berka and Adin Ballew. If you are looking for a website for your business
						|                                   you can contact us and speak with Adin about a site build.
		.box
			#contact(style='margin-top: 40px; margin-bottom: 40px; border-bottom: 1px solid #999;')
				center
					h1
						| Call us @ (918) 772-5101
